Maybe it is the diagonal that is supposed to be 1? This can be calculated with the Pythagorean theorem.


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
((-89.63298 - -89.32716)^2 + ( 37.39874 - 38.41781)^2)^0.5
